def count_cells_with_string(df, selected_string):
    count = 0
    for column in df.columns:
        count += df[column].str.contains(selected_string).sum()
    return count

def connect_type(my_list):
  a = []
  for i in my_list:
    result = count_cells_with_string(df_ev_connector_types, i)
    a.append(result)
    print("There are ", result, "EV stations have ",i, "connector types")
  print(a)

Conclusion¶

As we aim to find the factors which may affect on Australian EV charging station location, the top 3 important features of this dataset are facility_type, ev_pricing and ev_connector_type.
Based on this dataset, 14186 stations provide facility type information. 55.77% of them located in hotel(2803), car dealer(1910), garage or parking area(1703) and GOV (1495).
13492 EV charging stations provide price information. Among these stations, 75.3% stations are totally free, 23.3% stations ask for charging fee, 0.9% stations provide free charging service on specific condtion, 0.5% stations are free for charing but ask for parking fee.
57716 EV charing stations provide information about ev connector type. 94.75% of them have J1772 connector, 9.7% stations have TESLA connector, 9.43% J1772Combo connector, 8.52% have Chademo type.
